query:
SELECT id, employeeId, testType, discProfile, discDominance, discInfluence, discSteadiness, discCompliance, completedAt 
FROM psychometricTests 
WHERE testType = 'disc' 
ORDER BY completedAt DESC 
LIMIT 5;
